	<h4> Data and Methodology </h4>
	<p> Skatevideo soundtracks were scraped from <a href="skatevideosite.com">skatevideosite.com</a>. To give a more accurate view into music in popular skateboarding culture, videos not associated with established skateboarders or skateboarding companies were omitted. For example, music from a Bolivian skate-video produced by a group of friends wasn't included.
	<br><br>
	Because genre is <a href="https://pudding.cool/2017/03/punk/">hard to classify</a>, after feeding the artists through Spotify's API to get genre, I binned the genres into broader categories.
	<br><br>
	For the bubble chart, I only included artists featured at least four times in skate videos. This was done so that artists could more easily fit in the screen, as well as for performance reasons.
